## Next Steps
*   **Use Case Document:** Editors (Wes Eddy et al.) will bring open GitHub issues regarding group keying and asynchronous re-keying to the mailing list to reach a conclusion.
*   **Architecture Document:** Once adoption is confirmed, the authors will focus on refining the HTTP caching/identity text and incorporating feedback from Eric Rescorla.
*   **Future Meetings:** A dedicated discussion on addressing policy is anticipated for IETF 126 in Vienna.